dimensions.label: Forecast Lookup Niskanen Bridge
dimensions.name: forecast_lookup.niskanen_bridge
dimensions.sql:
CASE
          WHEN ${niskanen_forecast} = "safe_d" THEN "1 Solid Biden"
          WHEN ${niskanen_forecast} = "likely_d" THEN "2 Lean Biden"
          WHEN ${niskanen_forecast} = "tossup" THEN "3 Tossup"
          WHEN ${niskanen_forecast} = "likely_r" THEN "4 Lean Trump"
          WHEN ${niskanen_forecast} = "safe_r" THEN "5 Solid Trump"
          END

dimensions.label: Forecast Lookup Rough Forecast
dimensions.name: forecast_lookup.rough_forecast
dimensions.sql:
CASE
    WHEN ${forecast} = '1 Solid Biden' THEN '1 Biden'
    WHEN ${forecast} = '2 Lean Biden' THEN '1 Biden'
    WHEN ${forecast} = '4 Lean Trump' THEN '3 Trump'
    WHEN ${forecast} = '5 Solid Trump' THEN '3 Trump'
    ELSE '2 Tossup'
    END

measures.label: Margins Biden Win
measures.name: margins.biden_win
measures.sql:
CASE
          WHEN ${net_biden} >= 0 THEN 1
          ELSE null
    END

measures.label: Margins Forecast
measures.name: margins.forecast
measures.sql:
CASE
    WHEN ${fq_margin} >= 0 THEN '1 Solid Biden'
    WHEN ${fq_margin} < 0 AND ${median_margin} > 0 THEN '2 Lean Biden'
    WHEN ${tq_margin} > 0 AND ${median_margin} < 0 THEN '4 Lean Trump'
    WHEN ${tq_margin} <= 0 THEN '5 Solid Trump'
    WHEN ${median_margin} = 0 THEN '3 Tossup'
    ELSE '6 No Polling'
    END

measures.label: Margins Rough Forecast
measures.name: margins.rough_forecast
measures.sql:
CASE
          WHEN ${forecast} = '1 Solid Biden' THEN '1 Biden'
          WHEN ${forecast} = '2 Lean Biden' THEN '1 Biden'
          WHEN ${forecast} = '4 Lean Trump' THEN '3 Trump'
          WHEN ${forecast} = '5 Solid Trump' THEN '3 Trump'
          WHEN ${forecast} = '6 No Polling' THEN '4 Trump'
          ELSE '2 Tossup'
          END

measures.label: Margins Trump Win
measures.name: margins.trump_win
measures.sql:
CASE
          WHEN ${net_biden} <= 0 THEN 1
          ELSE null
    END
